!! Rn: HF cals with initial HF atomic orbitals : energy threshold=10^-8 : a smaller grid
title Rn  R = 3.0
method hf
nuclei  86.0 0.0 3.0
config  0
  1 phi                                                                           
  4 delta                                                                         
  9 pi                                                                            
  15 sigma end                                                                    
grid 295 40.0
orbpot hf 1
scf  4000 10 8 12 3
conv 1000
stop

